data.description: Expanded Bayhill model built by ''Award Winning'' Toll Brothers on  .3 acres with ample outdoor space. Open floor plan w/expanded Kitchen, Master Bedroom Suite with walk-in closet, and high ceilings throughout. The kitchen boasts granite counters, separate eating nook, breakfast bar, and sliding glass doors to a patio. Immaculately kept with newer appliances, recessed lighting, gas fireplace, custom molding, and a whole house generator. Bonus room for an office/gym, wash room w/sink, attic for storage, two car garage all in a prime location. Development offers state of the art clubhouse, gym, pool and tennis (pickle ball). Conveniently located to shopping and major roadways. This is a MUST SEE!
